Switch up s’mores this summer with a Triple Caramel Stroopwafel S’more! Pick your favorite Ghirardelli Caramel SQUARES and top a caramel stroopwafel with a marshmallow and Ghirardelli Caramel Sauce! It’s a caramel lovers dream! 😍 #SmoreCaramel #aBiteBetter 
Check out the link in our bio for the  recipe! 
📸 @thefeedfeed

Dipped Strawberries are the perfect Valentine’s Day treat! 🍓 See how easy it is to make dipped strawberries at home with Ghirardelli Melting Wafers using our recipe! Find the recipe link in our bio. ♥️

📸 @lmadesimple

These Dark Chocolate Dulce de Leche Sandwich Cookies are a delicious Valentine’s Day treat! 💕 They’re made with alternative ingredients like coconut milk and vegan butter along with our 72% Cacao Dark Chocolate Chips! Find the recipe with the link in our bio and bake them for someone special! #GhirardelliBaking #aBiteBetter 
📸 @thefeedfeed

Make your own Dark Chocolate Nut Butter Cups with quality chocolate. 😍 Ghirardelli 72% Cacao Dark Chocolate Chips let you control the sweetness in your treats! Find this recipe for and more with the link in our bio. ♥️ #GhirardelliBaking #aBiteBetter

Ghirardelli's 72% Cacao Dark Chocolate Chips are made with the highest quality cocoa beans for pure, rich dark chocolate. 😍 Use them in any recipe to control the level of sweetness like these delicious No-Bake Power Bites! #aBiteBetter #GhirardelliBaking

There’s nothing like a warm, freshly baked Chocolate Chip Cookie, especially if it’s made with Ghirardelli Chocolate! 🍪 Share special moments this holiday season and elevate your baking with Ghirardelli. #aBiteBetter #GhirardelliBaking Get the recipe on our IG story!
Everyone’s favorite Peppermint Bark is back with smooth layers of rich chocolate and festive peppermint! Share Ghirardelli and delight your family and friends this holiday season. ♥️ #aBiteBetter
